# Archive Messages (A) and some other nifty commands
bind editor <space> noop #fix for spaces in names of folders

bind index <Right> collapse-thread
#macro index <Down> "<enter-command>exec collapse-thread<return>;<enter-command>exec next-thread<return>;<enter-command>exec collapse-thread<return>"
#macro index <Up> "<enter-command>exec collapse-thread<return>;<enter-command>exec previous-thread<return>;<enter-command>exec collapse-thread<return>"
#folder-hook . "push <collapse-all><collapse-thread>"
